snippet.title: Gamma64 - Release & Download
snippet.description:
One year in the making, at last. Gamma64 is finally released to the public!!! I hope you all enjoy. Thank you so much for following me through my journey to create this hack!

Use a base US ROM to patch the game and run it!

Trailer made by MariHalo, his channel (subscribe!): https://www.youtube.com/c/MariHalo

ROMhacking.com page: https://romhacking.com/hack/gamma64
Download link: https://growalonegame.com/Gamma64_V1.10.zip
Gamma64 Discord Server: https://discord.gg/3wZpAFkf7J
